# Append-only logs: union-merge so parallel PRs adding entries to the same
# section (notably CHANGELOG.md's [Unreleased] block) auto-resolve instead of
# conflicting. A multi-PR drain otherwise hits N sequential CHANGELOG conflicts
# — every branch edits [Unreleased], and each merge shifts the block so later
# branches re-conflict (observed 4× in the v1.0.8-2 drain). `merge=union` keeps
# both sides' added lines; for an additive changelog that is exactly right.
CHANGELOG.md merge=union
RETRO.md merge=union
